### Description

The project doesn't compile again after the `src/index.html` changed 

### Minimal Reproduction

``` bash
npm i @angular/cui@17.3.8 -g
ng new ng17
npm start
```
After started, change `src/index.html` and save.



### Exception or Error

```text
The page of development (`http://localhost:4200`) had no change.
The command line had no new output after the `src/index.html` changed.
```

